name: seven blades
description:
This is Based on my nephew's dream.
he had a dream, he said if he wanted my business to be smooth and successful
I was advised to bury 7 knives in the yard.
the dream is weird but I'm between believing and not believing
and since then my business has been quiet
because in my area, especially in Java, black magic and magical things are still thick
and the point is because I believe in God more,
I just made this animation
